[ Lama Norbu Narrating ]
Mara had tried to tempt Siddhartha... in the cleverest of ways: by disguising the temptations of life... in the simplest forms.
But Siddhartha was looking beyond form, beyond the present.
And now
Mara was enraged.
[ All Gasping ]
