Dr. Verstak.
Yes, Macarthy.
Are you really a doctor?
Yes and no.
My husband is a medical doctor.
I'm Doctor of Philosophy.
I hurt no one.
Maybe I help.
Is wanting to survive so bad?
Susan.
Dear Susan.
Well... we made it.
Yes, we did.
Some of us.
